#Text=Tada
#Text=Tada is a town on the Chennai - Nellore highway , just over 65 km from Chennai , India and 80 km from Tirupathi .
#Text=It is in Nellore district of Andhra Pradesh and is about 1.5 km north of the Andhra Pradesh border .
#Text=Get in
#Text=This place marks the border of Andhra Pradesh .
#Text=Its nearest major railway station is Tada and Sullurpeta .
#Text=NH-5 starts from Chennai to Kolkata , which passes through Tada .
#Text=Pulicat Lake lies east to Tada .
#Text=Tada is well connected to Chennai via local trains and Mofussil buses that head to Chennai from Tirupathi and Nellore .
#Text=Trains from Chennai heading to Sullurpeta from Chennai Central pass via Tada .
#Text=There is a train every two hours and the last train from Tada to Chennai leaves at 8:30PM .
#Text=See
#Text=The Tada Falls - Also known as Ubbalamadugu Falls , which is about 15 km from the Tada railway station is a major attraction .
#Text=Since there are not many trek-worthy spots near Chennai , Tada falls has become a popular trekking spot for adventure enthusiasts from Chennai .
#Text=To reach the falls you had to take the road that goes west before the TADA town .
#Text=And ask for the village Varadayyapalem .
#Text=From here the falls would be nearly 5 km .
#Text=On the road from NH5 to Varadayyapalem is the Kalki Oneness Temple .
#Text=The Oneness Temple - Kalki Oneness Temple , in the Golden City , Varadaiahpalem , Chittoor Dist .
#Text=Andhra Pradesh , India : Just 3 km from small town Tada .
#Text=Do
#Text=Tada is a relatively little known tourist destination .
#Text=It is known for its waterfall ( locally called as Ubbalamadugu Falls ) , hillocks and greenery .
#Text=It is ideal for hiking , trekking and picnics .
#Text=Work

#Text=Tada is at a walking distance from Sri City , a Planned Integrated Business City ( Township ) located 55 km North of Chennai on NH 5 along the border of Andhra Pradesh ( AP ) and Tamil Nadu ( TN ) States of India .
#Text=Much of Sricity area is in Chittoor District and a smaller area along the NH5 is in Nellore District of AP , adjacent to Tiruvallur District of TN .
#Text=90+
#Text=top companies from around the globe are on board to set up shops at Sri City .

#Text=The Satish Dhawan Space Centre ( aka SHAR ) , India ’s Satellite/Rocket launching centre is located at Sriharikota , on the eastern side of the Pulicat Lake which separates Sri City and the Satellite launching station .
#Text=Sleep
#Text=Hotel
#Text=Rishi Gardens has nice food and also very good accommodation .
#Text=Tented accommodation is available near Tada . +918333008877
#Text=Otherwise , Sullurpeta has very good AC and non-AC lodges .
#Text=For better hotels
#Text=the best locations to stay are at Srikalahasti or Varadaiahpalem town .
